name: Long Term View on Longevity: A Chat with Dave Gobel
description:
Informal freeform conversation about anything in longevity, with Dave Gobel, co-founder of the Methuselah Foundation.


May chat about the last 25 years in longevity, prizes, biomarkers, humans on a chip, full body model, zk, philanthropy, OODA; may also chat about something else entirely.  We don't know until we starts talking.
